version_description: The whole song is a repetition and variation of the Intro. In the Outro just strum the E chord, make some variations you want to, and have fun with this marvelous song.
David Bowie - Slip Away (Live) - No Capo - Link https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQrJE56oU7I.
Easy song for beginners to sing and play.
The others have missed some chord changes.
